<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='2609:2632'>玉人云榖圭七寸天子以聘女注云納徴加於束帛賈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='2632:2656'>釋云自士已上皆用𤣥纁束帛但天子加以榖圭諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='2656:2679'>加大璋亦七寸典瑞云榖圭以和難以聘女後鄭云榖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='2679:2702'>圭亦王使之瑞節也榖善也其飾若粟文然仇讎和之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='2702:2725'>者若春秋宣公及齊侯平莒及郯晉侯使瑕嘉平戎於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='2725:2737'>王也其聘女則以納徴焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='2737:2764'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '010-15a' );" name="010-15a" class="pb">[010-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
