<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='3500:3523'>玉人云琬圭九寸而繅以象徳後鄭云琬猶圓也王使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='3523:3546'>之瑞節也諸侯有徳王命賜之使者執琬圭以致命焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='3546:3569'>故典瑞云琬圭以治德結好治徳即玉人注云諸侯有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='3569:3592'>徳王命賜之也結好謂諸侯使大夫來聘既而為壇㑹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='3592:3615'>之使大夫執以命事焉大行人曰時聘以結諸侯之好</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='3615:3634'>繅藉也先鄭云琬圭無鋒芒故治徳以結好</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='3634:3661'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '010-19a' );" name="010-19a" class="pb">[010-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
